        "content": "ðŸ“Š WORKFLOW START\n\nThis workflow monitors Jira Epics and calculates health scores:\n\nâ€¢ Runs every 6 hours\nâ€¢ Fetches all Epics\nâ€¢ Analyzes linked issues\nâ€¢ Calculates health metrics\nâ€¢ Flags at-risk epics\nâ€¢ Updates dashboards\nâ€¢ Alerts team via Slack"
