        "content": "ðŸ“¥ EPIC RETRIEVAL\n\nFetches all Epics from Jira:\n\nâ€¢ Uses Jira REST API\nâ€¢ getAll operation\nâ€¢ Retrieves: Epic keys, names, fields\nâ€¢ Filters to Epics only\n\nReturns list of all Epics in project\nPassed to Split Epics for processing"
