        "height": 316,
        "content": "ðŸ”€ SPLIT EPICS\n\nTransforms Epic batch into individual items:\n\nâ€¢ Iterates through each Epic\nâ€¢ Extracts Epic key\nâ€¢ Creates separate object per Epic\nâ€¢ Enables sequential processing\n\nInput: Array of Epics\nOutput: Individual Epic objects with key\n\nAllows detailed analysis per Epic"
